      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments use the same pump geometry, fluid, and operating envelope as the intended COU.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump — the identical geometry used in the COU — with physiologically representative blood analogue under CPB flow and speed conditions."
