      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; input parameter values are sourced from published literature and match experimental conditions.",
      "rationale": "Blood viscosity, density, and hemolysis power-law coefficients are taken from published FDA-cited sources; sensitivity to input variation is not formally quantified at MRL 2 but inputs are documented and traceable."
