    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are explicitly scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 guidance for Class II devices at MRL 2. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. The Requirement document (bindsRequirement) and Claim document (bindsClaim) contain the full narrative context of use, including patient population, operating envelope, and intended regulatory submission scope.",
